<Layout title="Contact" description="Contact information for the Master Mariners Benevolent Association archive. Historical officer listing and maritime community connections.">

  <div class="hero-band">
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p>MMBA historical contacts and maritime community connections</p>
  </div>

  <main>
    <h1>Contact &amp; Officers</h1>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Archive Notice</h3>
      <p>
        This website is maintained as a <strong>historical archive</strong>. The contact information below reflects the association's leadership as historically documented. We are not affiliated with any current organization operating under the Master Mariners name.
      </p>
      <p>For current maritime organizations in the San Francisco Bay Area, please see our <a href="/links">maritime links directory</a>.</p>
    </div>

